s that perform the required conversions for newly registered instance-store images in 4.0.\r\n\r\n*Pending object store upgrade is ready*: There is a data dependency on the objects containing the bundled image data.\r\n\r\n*Sketch of approach*:  Much like {{RegisterImage}} marks a registeration as {{pending_conversion}}, \r\n* Old instance-store images will be classified and, as needed, marked as {{pending_upgrade}}.  \r\n* The same mechanisms for registering will be used to create and process the conversions.   \r\n* Completion of conversion makes the corresponding {{EMI}} ready for use by transitioning it to {{available}}.\r\n* For some {{EMI}}s RunInstances will not be affected. \r\n\r\nh4. Next Steps\r\n* *[~dmitrii]* will raise flag (here and/or email) when needed register mechanisms are ready.\r\n* Determine best behaviour system should have while image conversion upgrade is ongoing.\r\n* Cloud may appear down in certain cases, e.g., if there are many of these converting.","customfield_13000":null,"customfield_13200":null,"customfield_11300":null,"customfield_11500":null,"timetracking":{},"customfield_10401":null,"customfield_10600":null,"customfield_12900":null,"attachment":[],"aggregatetimeestimate":null,"summary":"Upgrade and conversion of partition based instance store images to operational format","creator":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=decker","name":"decker","key":"decker","accountId":"557058:518b1ab0-12c2-4e72-b694-6c07036941a8","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a84cbf1ecec07d9320b42ae4fc90ccce?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Ddecker%26avatarId%3D16203%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a84cbf1ecec07d9320b42ae4fc90ccce?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Ddecker%26avatarId%3D16203%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a84cbf1ecec07d9320b42